About Ignite Restaurant Group, Inc.
Ignite Restaurant Group, Inc., headquartered in Houston, Texas, operates a portfolio of restaurant brands, including Joe's Crab Shack and Brick House Tavern + Tap, in a diverse set of markets across the United States. Each brand offers a variety of high-quality food in a distinctive, casual, high-energy atmosphere.



